      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="Georg_Brandes_arkiv_144"/>Herrn Prof. <hi rend="latintype">Georg
                     Brandes</hi></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb182" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Paris</hi></rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb1095" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Hotel Lutetia</hi></rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb1094" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Boulevrd Pasqual</hi></rs></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="image"><p rend="center"><pb facs="Georg_Brandes_arkiv_143"/><hi rend="pre-print"><rs ref="#pmb667" type="place">Garmisch</rs> geg. <rs type="place" ref="#pmb92079">Wetterstein</rs></hi></p></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline><pb facs="Georg_Brandes_arkiv_144"/><rs ref="#pmb667" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Partenkirchen</hi></rs>, <date>29. 4. 11</date></dateline></opener><p>Ihre Karte, <salute>verehrter Herr Br<damage agent="paperloss"><supplied>andes,</supplied></damage></salute> und die Druck<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chriften<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ind uns nach <rs ref="#pmb36456" type="place">Mentone</rs> nachgewandert, u. am Ende meiner Rei<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>e, dank ich und grüß ich
               herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t in alter Treue.</p><closer>Ihr<lb/><signed>Arth Schni</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
